_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27705:\"\n<p>The importance of creative agencies can’t be stressed enough and creativity is the core of any successful marketing campaign. &nbsp;Apart from helping you build your brand, creative agencies play a major role in improving your organization’s public perception. Most Creative Digital Agencies are recognizing the importance of having well-designed websites. But even an established Creative Agency might need a little help with website customization. The good news is that WordPress has made it possible for Digital Agencies to create websites using the platform. WordPress is popular due to its ease of use and the availability of thousands of themes and plugins to choose from. Great Digital Agency WordPress themes can do much more than just helping you create an attractive website.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are thousands of competitively priced Digital Agency WordPress themes in the market, and new ones are being developed every day. Choosing the right theme that will enhance and remodel your site from the several ones available is no picnic. But worry not. We have done extensive research to present you 13 of the Best Digital Agency WordPress Themes in 2020. All the themes on our list are up-to-date, have practical features specifically intended for your Creative Agency, are Responsive and SEO Friendly to achieve an Agency’s Conversion Goals.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Without further ado, here are our top selections for the best Creative Agency WordPress themes.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Studio 8</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme/\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-8.jpg\" alt=\"Studio 8 - WordPress Theme for Photography\" class=\"wp-image-20674\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-8.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-8-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-8-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-8-1024x817.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-8-600x479.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></a><figcaption> Studio 8 &#8211; WordPress Theme for Photography</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Another feature-rich theme by WPlook Themes, Studio 8 shares pretty much the same features and style as the two Digital Agency WordPress themes above. It is a flexible, appealing and profoundly functional theme designed for Creative Professionals, Agencies, Architects, Web Designers, and Filmmakers. The theme has an attractive and professional layout and since it’s a theme from WPlook, you can be sure that the conversions are well taken care of. As you scroll through Studio 8, you will note the various ways you can promote your agency’s services and build credibility with potential clients.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Studio 8 is coming with 11 Gutenberg Blocks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This theme will hook your visitors and make them stay on your website for extended periods. Studio 8 is Multilingual Ready to cater to your non-English speaking audience. This theme is fully responsive and compatible with all devices and browsers. Take advantage of the Unlimited Color Schemes to pick a color that is consistent with your brand’s identity. Installation takes just about 3 minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Learn More about Studio 8</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/host/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=32&amp;customfield[8]=Studio 8&amp;billingcycle=triennially\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Host This Theme From $5.42/m\">Host This Theme From $5.42/m</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Studio 9</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/studio-9-wordpress-theme-for-freelancers/\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9.jpg\" alt=\"Studio 9 - WordPress Theme for Photographs\" class=\"wp-image-20673\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9-1024x817.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/studio-9-600x479.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></a><figcaption> Studio 9 &#8211; WordPress Theme for Photographs</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Studio 9 is an elegant, conceptually designed and easy-to-install theme for Agencies, Freelancers, Web Designers, Photographers and Creative Professionals. Studio 9 has an impressive and modern aesthetic that will appeal to your audience. This theme is meant for anyone who wants to achieve a great looking online presence. Studio 9 WordPress theme is extremely fast, has a responsive design and is cross-browser compatible making it look good across multiple devices.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can keep your audience engaged by publishing articles and showcasing your recent projects. The Shortcodes Plugin in this 5-star theme will enable you to customize your website easily. Thanks to the WooCommerce integration, you can easily turn your site into an online store and handle payments, shipping and inventory conveniently.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/studio-9-wordpress-theme-for-freelancers/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Learn More about Studio 9</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/host/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=32&amp;customfield[8]=Studio 9&amp;billingcycle=triennially\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Host This Theme From $5.42/m\">Host This Theme From $5.42/m</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Agency</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/agency-wordpress-theme/\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-agency-1024x817.jpg\" alt=\"The Agency - Digital Creative WordPress Theme\" class=\"wp-image-21040\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-agency-1024x817.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-agency-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-agency-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-agency-600x479.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-agency.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a><figcaption> The Agency &#8211; Digital Creative WordPress Theme</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The Agency is a theme you can trust to promote your agency with and grow your brand. A quick look at this theme will wow your audience and help to pass your message to them.&nbsp;What makes The Agency stand out is its outstanding design 3 Widget Areas and 2 Custom Post Types that will make your content capture the interest of your online visitors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Studio 8 is coming with 10 Gutenberg Blocks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Primarily designed for Web Designers and Architect, The Agency will help you present your team, showcase your projects and keep your audience updated on the latest happenings.&nbsp;This must-have theme presents your web visitors with crisp typography that will definitely grab their attention.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/agency-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Learn More about The Agency</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/host/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=32&amp;customfield[8]=The Agency&amp;billingcycle=triennially\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Host This Theme From $5.42/m\">Host This Theme From $5.42/m</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>The SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/SEO.jpg\" alt=\"The SEO - Digital Marketing Agency WordPress Theme\" class=\"wp-image-21041\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/SEO.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/SEO-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/SEO-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/SEO-1024x817.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/SEO-600x479.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption> The SEO &#8211; Digital Marketing Agency WordPress Theme</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have been unsuccessfully searching for a Digital Marketing Agency WordPress theme with a minimalist and straightforward design, look no further than The SEO. This is an adaptable theme that will enable you to create a proficient looking website. Whether you are an Internet Marketer, Social Media Marketer or a Lead Generation Expert, you will find this SEO optimized theme useful for your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With 100+ pages with examples, 700+ Google Fonts, 400+ SEO Services Icons and 4 Header Types and a one-click installer, creating an agency website has never been this simple. Make use of the Drag and Drop Page builder to customize your blog how you want it. The Unlimited Colors will allow you to pick a color that fits your brand.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://1.envato.market/c/1288490/275988/4415?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthemeforest.net%2Fitem%2Fthe-seo-seo-and-digital-marketing-agency-wordpress-theme%2F13870880\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about The SEO</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Pile</h2>\n\n\