erce plugin, and custom widgets and modules to spice up your website’s design. You can additionally throw in a few elements and multiple page layouts to create attractive pages. The right jewelry theme will make your jewels appear even more expensive and luxurious.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Considering all the requirements we have mentioned above, it can be time-consuming to find the right jewelry theme online. We have done extensive research to present you a collection of the finest Premium Jewelry WordPress Themes in 2018. Premium themes are designed by professional developers and have a higher stability, better performance, round-the-clock support lines and extra features- things you won’t find in a free theme. We always try to keep our lists short, so only the best themes reside here.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Nitro</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/nitro.jpg\" alt=\"Nitro - WooCommerce Theme\" class=\"wp-image-22015\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/nitro.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/nitro-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/nitro-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/nitro-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/nitro-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Nitro &#8211; WooCommerce Theme</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nitro is the headliner in our list. It is a dynamic, adaptable, powerful and universal WooCommerce Theme that is the absolute best choice for your jewelry business. Nitro will fine tune your design and help you build an incredible eCommerce store for your jewelry business. Notable features include robust performance, intuitive design, wide-ranging shortcodes and eCommerce functionalities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This theme is compatible with the latest version of WooCommerce and WordPress. eCommerce features include Product Photo Zoom, Sales Countdown, Product Quick View, Buy Now Button and Product Image Hover Effect. The only way to truly see what Nitro has to offer is by giving it a try. You will love the results!</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://1.envato.market/c/1288490/275988/4415?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthemeforest.net%2Fitem%2Fnitro-universal-woocommerce-theme-from-ecommerce-experts%2F15761106\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Nitro</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jewellery</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/jewelery.jpg\" alt=\"Jewellery - WooCommerce Responsive Theme\" class=\"wp-image-22023\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/jewelery.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/jewelery-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/jewelery-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/jewelery-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/jewelery-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Jewellery &#8211; WooCommerce Responsive Theme</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Jewelry is an attractive and multipurpose eCommerce WordPress theme best suited for jewelry, fashion,&nbsp;and apparel related business. This theme allows webmasters to have full control over its features and layout without touching a single line of code. Jewelry has a clean and exquisite design that will help your eCommerce store look appealing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you buy Jewelry theme, you will enjoy features such as FREE Lifetime Updates and On-Going Support, Unlimited Color Options, Unlimited Banners and Sliders, 1500 + Font Awesome ICONS, Cross-Browser compatibility and Full User Guide Documentation. Use Jewelry with all the skills at your disposal to reach new clients and keep the old ones coming back.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://1.envato.market/c/1288490/275988/4415?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthemeforest.net%2Fitem%2Fjewellery-woocommerce-responsive-theme%2F8778747\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Jewellery</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Luxury</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-luxuary.jpg\" alt=\"The Luxury - Dark/Light Responsive WordPress Theme\" class=\"wp-image-22026\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-luxuary.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-luxuary-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-luxuary-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-luxuary-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/the-luxuary-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>The Luxury &#8211; Dark/Light Responsive WordPress Theme</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There is no doubt in mind that The Luxury WordPress Theme is one of the classiest eCommerce WordPress theme in the market currently. The Luxury is a graceful, radiant and entertaining eCommerce WordPress theme perfect for your online jewelry store. You can use it to sell luxury products such as jewelry, watches, bags, yachts\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_11 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"11\" data-gr-id=\"11\">and</g> cars. You get the award-winning Master Slider to manage slider’s elements valued at $28 for free.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can turn your website into anything you want thanks to Unlimited Color Options. The collections of Awesome Shortcodes will empower your eCommerce store and keep your online visitors glued to your jewelry store. On purchase, you get full access to Premium Support. This Dark/Light Responsive WP Theme has much more in store for you, so try it out today!</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://1.envato.market/c/1288490/275988/4415?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthemeforest.net%2Fitem%2Fthe-luxury-darklight-responsive-wordpress-theme%2F9210438\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about The Luxury</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Basel</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/basel.jpg\" alt=\"Basel - Responsive eCommerce Theme\" class=\"wp-image-22030\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/basel.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/basel-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/basel-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/basel-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/basel-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Basel &#8211; Responsive eCommerce Theme</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Basel is an insanely creative, AJAX responsive and flexible eCommerce Jewelry WordPress theme that allows web designers and developers to create unique store layouts. Developed with CSS3, Basel is suitable for any type of shop like jewelry, electronics, cloth, accessories, flowers\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_9 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"9\" data-gr-id=\"9\">and</g> furniture just to mention a few.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead of taking our word for it, you can use both Basel and your imagination to craft an awe-inspiring eCommerce store that will keep your clients coming back. Basel is compatible with popular WP plugins like Contact form 7, MailChimp, WishList Plugin and Revolution Slider. Basel is also optimized for hand-held devices as well as SEO purposes.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://1.envato.market/c/1288490/275988/4415?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthemeforest.net%2Fitem%2Fbasel-responsive-ecommerce-theme%2F14906749\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Basel</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Polaris</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/polaris.jpg\" alt=\"Polaris — Minimal &amp; Powerful Multipurpose WooCommerce Theme\" class=\"wp-image-22036\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/polaris.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/polaris-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/polaris-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/polaris-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/polaris-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Polaris — Minimal &amp; Powerful Multipurpose WooCommerce Theme</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Polaris is a vibrant, modern and eye-pleasing multipurpose eCommerce WordPress theme designed specifically for eCommerce Trading. This theme is suitable for both beginners and advanced webmasters. The user- friendly and intuitive admin panel in Polaris means that you do not require any coding knowledge to navigate this theme.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Drag and Drop Functionality will help you customize your jewelry store easily. Polaris Future Proof responsive design was developed with the current modern devices in mind. Other powerful features are 5 Pre-built Unique Styled Demos, Live Search Functions, and Filters, 1 Click Demo Import and 6 Months Expert Support.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://1.envato.market/c/1288490/275988/4415?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthemeforest.net%2Fitem%2Fpolaris-minimal-powerful-multipurpose-woocommerce-theme%2F12098983\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Polaris</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Pablo Guadi</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/pabloguardi.jpg\" alt=\"Pablo Guadi - Jewelry Designer &amp; Handcrafted Jewelry Online Shop \" class=\"wp-image-22041\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/pabloguardi.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/pabloguardi-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/pabloguardi-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/pabloguardi-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/pabloguardi-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Pablo Guadi &#8211; Jewelry Designer &amp; Handcrafted Jewelry Online Shop </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you own an online business that sells jewelry and you are looking forward gaining more recognition and conquer the industry, look no further than Pablo Guadi. This theme is a competent, versatile and chic Jewelry Designer and Handcrafted Jewelry Online Shop WordPress Theme. It is best suited for online stores offering jewelry, artwork, accessories, crafts, and handmade creative goods.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The friendly user interface and informative layout in Pablo Guadi mean that your eCommerce store will look good on any platform. Built with valid CSS3 and HTML5 code, this theme is loaded with options and tools meant to help you create a complete website under a short time. Pablo Guadi is fully equipped with WPBakery Page Builder, Revolution Slider, PO Composer and Essential Grid.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://1.envato.market/c/1288490/275988/4415?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthemeforest.net%2Fitem%2Fpablo-gu