\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"photo editor apps\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wplook.com/?p=20286\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:565:\"<p>High-quality images are an invaluable part of the online content, they give your website a more professional look. As a designer, you probably have an extensive archive of images that need refining with photo editor apps. Editing images before uploading them online is an essential step as it enables you to adjust sharpness, color, white [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/photo-editor-apps/\">The 10 Best Photo Editor Apps to Use in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Diana\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20392:\"\n<p>High-quality images are an invaluable part of the online content, they give your website a more professional look. As a designer, you probably have an extensive archive of images that need refining with photo editor apps. Editing images before uploading them online is an essential step as it enables you to adjust sharpness, color, white balance, exposure and more. This way, you can reproduce the image you saw in your mind when you took the photo. MacOS and Windows both have built-in photo editing apps that come in handy for quick edits. You will, however, need to consider a more powerful editor for complex edits. As a designer, you need an app that will do more than just import, organize and render photos.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are several web-based photo editor software at your disposal. For a more professional outcome, you need to embrace desktop and smartphone apps. These apps help you to make the most out of the latest photo-editing techniques and offer you ways to organize and share your photos easily.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Standard features in these photo editor apps include:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Lens distortion adjustment<br> 2. Vector graphic tools<br> 3. Wide-ranging filter effects<br> 4. Paint and drawing options<br> 5. Shadow and highlight adjustment options<br> 6. RAW converters<br> 7. In-built photo organizers</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adobe Photoshop leads the pack as the most widely-used photo editing software among the design community. So much is its popularity that the word Photoshop has been verbified, just like Google. Publishers release new versions of their flagship photo editor apps annually to give them new and improved features and tools. We are in the second quarter of 2020, and it’s the perfect time to check out some of the latest apps for the year. The many photo-editing alternatives can overwhelm you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This article has rounded up 10 of the Best Photo Editor Apps across an array of platforms and budgets. We took into account ease of use, customer support, creative freedom, sharing options, functionality, price and community reviews. We hope that by the end of our detailed analysis, you will be able to pick the right app for your needs.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Affinity Photo&nbsp;<strong>($49.99)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/affinity-1024x540.jpg\" alt=\"Affinity Photo Editor Apps\" class=\"wp-image-20288\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/affinity-1024x540.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/affinity-300x158.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/affinity-768x405.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/affinity.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/affinity-600x317.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Affinity Photo Editor Apps</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are intimidated by Photoshop and hate subscriptions, Serif’s Affinity Photo is the ideal app for you. Affinity Photo’s menu, layer tools, workflow, digital painting and batch tools are easy to master. This exciting image editor is available on Mac and also compatible with Windows 7/8/10. Their latest update, the Affinity Photo 5 has an impressive 57 customizable filter effects and over 120 brushes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This software is the perfect image combining editor. It also fully supports Photoshop files. A one-off payment of $50 is all you need to start using this amazing software. The price is a relative bargain when compared to other image editors in this list. It is available on iOS, macOS\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_9 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"9\" data-gr-id=\"9\">, </g>and Windows.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Has an extensive list of tools for in-depth edits<br> • Stunning real-time effects<br> • Easy-to-navigate interface<br> • PSD import/export<br> • Supports 360<sup>°</sup> and RAW image editing<br> • One-time payment<br> • Dozens of tutorials on their dedicated YouTube channel</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://affinity.serif.com/en-us/photo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Affinity Photo</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>GIMP ( Free)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gimp-1024x594.jpg\" alt=\"GNU Image Manipulation Program (GIMP)\" class=\"wp-image-20289\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gimp-1024x594.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gimp-300x174.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gimp-768x445.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gimp.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/gimp-600x348.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> GNU Image Manipulation Program (GIMP)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>GIMP is a desktop-oriented, open-source photo editor. The app is widely called as the best open-source alternative to Adobe Photoshop. This is because it has most of the advanced editing and image-enhancing tools present in Photoshop. I highly recommend GIMP to designers working on a tight budget looking for an app with the right balance of power and flexibility. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The multi-platform photo editing app is compatible with Linux, Mac OS X\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_6 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"6\" data-gr-id=\"6\">, </g>and Windows. The layer feature means that you can easily combine your pictures to your liking. You can use this software to edit all photo formats. GIMP has a large community of active supporters (both users and developers) that help to improve the app regularly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• No limitations or ads<br> • High-quality photo manipulation<br> • A variety of advanced options<br> • User-friendly interface<br> • Supports programming algorithms such as C, C++, Python and Perl</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.gimp.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about GIMP</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Pixelmator PRO (</strong>$59.99)</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pixel-1024x616.jpg\" alt=\"Pixelmator Pro\" class=\"wp-image-20290\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pixel-1024x616.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pixel-300x181.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pixel-768x462.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pixel.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pixel-600x361.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Pixelmator Pro</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If your editing style is less intensive, Pixelmator PRO is the right option for you. Pixelmator is a detailed, professional editing software that is easy to download and install on your Mac. Based on a combination of open-source and Mac OS X, it is a household name in the Mac world especially for beginners and semi-pro designers. The app uses Mac OS X to empower you to edit photos just like Photoshop.</p>\n\n\n\n<p> It is not as well knows as Adobe Photoshop or GIMP, but it is another high ranking photo editor app packed with 40+ advanced image-enhancing tools to make editing faster and more intuitive. Save your images in a format of your choice including PNG, PDF, PSD and TIFF. Its built-in export tools allow you to post edited images to Facebook and Flickr conveniently. The interface has been recently updated to make it more Mac friendly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Provides fantastic tools for manipulation<br> • Editing photos require minimum effort<br> • It supports vector graphics<br> • Has touch bar optimization</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://www.pixelmator.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Pixelmator</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Photoshop CC&nbsp;(Different plans for individuals, businesses, students and schools)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/photoshop-cc-1024x582.jpg\" alt=\"Photoshop CC\" class=\"wp-image-20291\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/photoshop-cc-1024x582.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/photoshop-cc-300x171.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/photoshop-cc-768x436.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/photoshop-cc.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/photoshop-cc-600x341.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Photoshop CC</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Photoshop is the benchmark for all the other photo editor apps. The Photoshop CC app works like magic and provides users with a decent toolset for editing images. There is no end to the possibilities available with Photoshop CC. This 2018 edition comes with a new auto-select tool, a variety of font and drawing capabilities and raw camera profiles. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>With this program, you can draw magnificent drawings, create great paintings, design banners and logos etc. Available for both PCs and Macs, the only downsides to this head-bangingly brilliant app is monthly subscriptions and complex interface for beginners.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Step-by-step tutorials<br> • Copy and paste shortcut<br> • Color and luminance range masking<br> • Ability to access Lightroom Photos</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Photoshop</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Handy Photo (</strong>$2.99<strong>)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/handy-photo-1024x528.jpg\" alt=\"Handy Photo\" class=\"wp-image-20292\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/handy-photo-1024x528.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/handy-photo-300x155.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/handy-photo-768x396.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/handy-photo.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/handy-photo-600x310.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Handy Photo</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Handy Photo is one of the hottest all-in-one photo editor apps that packs impressive features. It has a fantastic interface designed for creative designers to develop awe-inspiring images. Handy Photo’s editing and organizing abilities are well complemented by its range of powerful tools that allow you to add effects and work on layers. A product of ADVA Soft, it has a gentle learning curves for beginners.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Simple to use<br> • Remarkably versatile<br> • Powerful photo filters<br> • Magic crop feature</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://adva-soft.com/products/handy-photo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Handy Photo</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Snapseed (Free)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/snapseed-1024x785.jpg\" alt=\"Snapseed Photo Editor App\" class=\"wp-image-20293\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/snapseed-1024x785.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/snapseed-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/snapseed-768x589.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/snapseed-600x460.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/snapseed.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Snapseed Photo Editor App</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Snapseed is a straightforward and fun photo editor app that heavily relies on gestures to select and control a plethora of filters and other tools. Snapseed’s simplicity is one of its major selling points. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The complete photo editing software has multiple features that will help you with picture enhancement, photo composition and retouching. It is easy to download and install, and it can be used on both iOS and Android operating systems.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Minimal learning curve<br> • Updated regularly<br> • Selective filter brush<br> • Supports both PNG and JPG files</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.niksoftware.snapseed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Snapseed</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Picmonkey&nbsp;$5.99/$8.99 (free 7-day trial)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pickmonkey-1024x606.jpg\" alt=\"PicMonkey\" class=\"wp-image-20294\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pickmonkey-1024x606.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pickmonkey-300x178.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pickmonkey-768x454.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pickmonkey.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/pickmonkey-600x355.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> PicMonkey</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>PicMonkey is another highly-rated photo editor app that comes with a complete graphic design package. This makes this web-based software fun and easy to edit images, crop them, make collages, touch up and more. The app can also be used on mobile devices. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is compatible with both Android and iOS. If you are looking for a photo editor that will help you develop your design skills and help you attain your full potential, you should definitely try out PicMonkey. Overall, PicMonkey is an invaluable tool that can produce stunning results in the hands of a gifted designer.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Offers 4 editing modes<br> • You can print directly from PicMonkey<br> • Has eye-catching designer-made templates<br> • Includes premium fonts and special effects</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.picmonkey.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about PicMonkey</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Befunky (Free)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/befuk-1024x623.jpg\" alt=\"Befunky\" class=\"wp-image-20296\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/befuk-1024x623.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/befuk-300x183.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/befuk-768x467.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/befuk.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/befuk-600x365.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Befunky</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Befunky might appear like a rather simple photo editor, but take a closer look at the main menu and you will discover a wealth of features: pull-out menu and in-built effects. What really sets Befunky from alternative photo editor apps is that it portability that allows you to upload photos from almost anywhere. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This app includes most of the essential editing tools for designers. It will help bring out your creativity to edit photos proficiently before sharing them online. You can use it online or on your iOS or Android-powered smartphone.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Advanced photo effects<br> • Hundreds of fonts to choose from<br> • Full-screen workspace<br> • Supports up to 4k pixels square</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.befunky.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Befunky</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>VSCO (Free)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vsco-1024x676.jpg\" alt=\"VSCO\" class=\"wp-image-20297\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vsco-1024x676.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vsco-300x198.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vsco-768x507.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vsco.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/vsco-600x396.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> VSCO</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>VSCO is another powerful and intuitive photo editing and camera app tool for mobile devices. It is available for both Android and iOS. It was designed with a modern-photographer needs in mind. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Its minimalist interface enables you to get some terrific image output. It may be a little daunting for\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_5 gr-alert sel gr_spell gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"5\" data-gr-id=\"5\">entry-level</g> users. The all-new VSCO X has a 7-day Trial period and a one-off $19.99 payment.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Innovative camera controls<br> • You can easily share your images through the VSCO community<br> • Social media integration</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://vsco.co\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about VSCO</a>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>PaintShop Pro&nbsp; ($79.99)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/paintshop.jpg\" alt=\"PaintShop Pro\" class=\"wp-image-20298\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/paintshop.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/paintshop-300x185.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/paintshop-768x473.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/paintshop-1024x631.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/paintshop-600x370.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>PaintShop Pro</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Last but not least is PaintShop Pro. This user-friendly editor has a variety of advanced editing options, 86 creative filters and graphic design tools. PaintShop Pro is every designer’s dreams. It is packed with handy tools that will help you manipulate your images to your satisfaction. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Notable tools include lens correction fixes, photo organizer and fade correction tool. Graphic designers can make the most out of the many brushes and drawing tools. The standard plan goes at $79.99 and is compatible with Windows 7/8/10.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>• Automatic and hands-on editing tools<br> • Supports both vector and raster image formats<br> • Clean and organized interface<br> • Smart Photo Fix Tool that lets you compare images to make alterations</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.paintshoppro.com/en/products/paintshop-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about PaintShop Pro</a>\n\n\n\n<p>Conclusion</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are serious about design, you’re going to need more than the basic photo-editing tools a smartphone can provide. You need to rely on powerful desktop apps that make ordinary images look attractive. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best photo editor apps listed above have dedicated image editing suites that will allow you to do adjust just about everything in a photo. The best software depends on what exactly you need from it.<br> You might also consider reading the <a href=\"https://wplook.com/13-best-code-editors-available-2018/\">13 Best Code Editors Available in 2018</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/photo-editor-apps/\">The 10 Best Photo Editor Apps to Use in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/fZ6E4C7lC1E\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://wplook.com/photo-editor-apps/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://wplook.com/photo-editor-apps/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"8 Best WordPress Backup Plugins 2020\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wplook/~3/GHBl9yv_XHg/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-backup-plugins/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 11 Apr 2020 01:50:00 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Collections\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"WordPress performance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wplook.com/?p=23040\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:529:\"<p>Server crashes, hacking, simple user errors and dodgy updates may ruin your entire WordPress website causing you to lose all your data. It is for this reason that you need to invest in only the best WordPress Backup Plugins to ensure your content is secure at all times. To help you pick the best backup [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-backup-plugins/\">8 Best WordPress Backup Plugins 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Diana\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13518:\"\n<p>Server crashes, hacking, simple user errors and dodgy updates may ruin your entire WordPress website causing you to lose all your data. It is for this reason that you need to invest in only the best WordPress Backup Plugins to ensure your content is secure at all times.</p>\n\n\n\n<p> To help you pick the best backup plugin, we have put together this list of 8 of the best WordPress backup plugins.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Duplicator</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/duplicator.jpg\" alt=\"WordpRess Backup Plugins\" class=\"wp-image-23059\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/duplicator.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/duplicator-300x234.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/duplicator-768x599.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/duplicator-1024x799.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/duplicator-600x468.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Duplicator – WordPress Migration Plugin</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Duplicator is one of the most popular free WordPress backup plugins in the world with over 10 million downloads. This backup plugin not only serves as a simple backup utility, but it also lets users to copy, move, migrate and even clone a website from one server to another with zero downtime migrations. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It does this by bundling all a site’s themes, content, database, plugins and WordPress files into one simple zip file otherwise known as a package. Once it has all the necessary in the package, the WordPress site can then be easily migrated to the user’s location of preference. Whether you plan on moving it on the same server or across servers, as long as it can host a WordPress site, it can be moved anywhere.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Free&amp;Premium ($39)</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Duplicator Plugin </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>UpdraftPlus</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/updraft.jpg\" alt=\"UpdraftPlus\" class=\"wp-image-23099\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/updraft.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/updraft-300x165.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/updraft-768x421.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/updraft-1024x561.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/updraft-600x329.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>UpdraftPlus</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>UpdraftPlus is a free WordPress backup plugin that offers users a multitude of features to ensure easy and accurate backup. Users can gain access to more features for a seamless backup experience using their premium package. Some of these features include:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Cloning and Migration: Allows you to copy your entire WordPress website and move it to a new domain.</li><li>Scheduling: Allows you to set up backup schedules.</li><li>Customer Support: Offers fast, personal support from the development team.</li><li>Automatic pre-update backup: Automatically backs up your site before any updates are made.</li><li>It also backs up non-WordPress files and databases</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With this plugin, users can save their entire installation, including WordPress content for free. Once saved, they can push them to an external Backup Service like S3, FT, Dropbox among others. With a single backup zip file, users can easily restore an installation. This plugin offers both a free and a paid version.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin automatically uploads your backups to Google Drive, S3, Dropbox, SFTP, FTP, email among other cloud storage services.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free&amp;Premium($70)</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://updraftplus.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about UpdraftPlus Plugin </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>BlogVault</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/blogvault.jpg\" alt=\"wordpress backup plugin\" class=\"wp-image-23066\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/blogvault.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/blogvault-300x234.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/blogvault-768x599.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/blogvault-1024x799.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/blogvault-600x468.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>WordPress Backup &amp; Security Plugin – BlogVault</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With over 220,00 already using this WordPress backup plugin, it is among the most reliable backup and restores plugins today. This plugin guarantees users an easy to use WordPress backup and security solutions in one dashboard. All its backed up data is stored in a cloud which includes the Amazon S3 and Blogvault servers. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It also provides real-time backup for all wooCommerce sites. BlogVaulta also enables backup validation, migration, restore, site copying, dedicated staging, website management with no interruptions and upload to Dropbox. It uses SFTP, FTP or FTPS for the migrate function. BlogVaultal WordPress Plugin so boasts of one of the best-in-class malware scanning and removal functionality</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free&amp;Premium</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/blogvault-real-time-backup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about BlogVault Plugin </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>BackUpWordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backupwordpress.jpg\" alt=\"BackUpWordPress\" class=\"wp-image-23070\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backupwordpress.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backupwordpress-300x237.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backupwordpress-768x606.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backupwordpress-1024x808.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backupwordpress-600x474.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>BackUpWordPress</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The BackUpWordPress plugin can back up your entire site, including files and database on a schedule that best suits you. It is also quite easy to use, allowing even novices to navigate it without meeting any hurdles. It offers automatic scheduling allowing you to create different schedules for your files and database. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>BackUpWordPress offers both a free and a paid package. The free package, however, does not allow users to store their WordPress backups to a cloud. To get this service, users need to subscribe to the premium extension.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free&amp;Premium</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/backupwordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about BackUpWordPress Plugin </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Backup Guard</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-guard.jpg\" alt=\"WordPress Backup and Migrate Plugin – Backup Guard\" class=\"wp-image-23073\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-guard.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-guard-300x234.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-guard-768x599.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-guard-1024x799.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-guard-600x468.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>WordPress Backup and Migrate Plugin – Backup Guard</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is one of the easiest WordPress backup plugins that allows users to backup, migrate and restore their WordPress websites including the database and files. This plugin offers both a free and paid services. Some of its best features include customizable backups, supports multi sites and restore feature.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Backup Guard Pro helps you to migrate in all of these cases in the smoothest possible way. You just have to Backup your site and Restore it in the new location. No additional work will be required\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_6 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-del replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"6\" data-gr-id=\"6\"></g> since we handle all changes for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Free&amp;Premium($19.95)</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/backup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Backup Guard Plugin </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>VaultPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backups@2x.jpg\" alt=\"VaultPress\" class=\"wp-image-23082\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backups@2x.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backups@2x-300x216.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backups@2x-768x553.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backups@2x-1024x737.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backups@2x-600x432.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>VaultPress</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>VaultPress is a real-time WordPress Backup plugin and security scanning service. This plugin is designed and built by Automattic- the company that operates and backs up millions of sites on WordPress.com. It is powered by Jetpack and easily backs up all posts, comments, media files, revision and dashboard settings on your site to their server. This plugin also protects you from malware, accidental damage, host outages, and hackers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free&amp;Premium ($39)</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/vaultpress/#description\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about VaultPress Plugin </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>BackupBuddy</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-23163\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-300x183.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-768x469.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-1024x625.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backup-600x367.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>BackupBuddy</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>BackupBuddy not only backs up your WordPress database but also your entire WordPress installation to ensure you always have a copy of all your WordPress website files. It also includes everything you need to successfully run a WordPress website. With this plugin, you can backup all your WordPress files, plugins, themes and all files in the media library. &nbsp;Once the backup process is complete you will get a downloadable zip file of your WordPress website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: $80</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://ithemes.com/purchase/backupbuddy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about BackupBuddy Plugin </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>BackWPup</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backwp.jpg\" alt=\"BackWPup – WordPress Backup Plugin\" class=\"wp-image-23095\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backwp.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backwp-300x221.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backwp-768x565.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backwp-1024x753.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/backwp-600x442.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>BackWPup – WordPress Backup Plugin</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With this plugin, users can save their entire installation, including WordPress content for free. Once saved, they can push them to an external Backup Service like S3, FT, Dropbox among others. With a single backup zip file, users can easily restore an installation. This plugin offers both a free and a paid version. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Price: Free&amp;Premium $69.00</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/backwpup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about BackWPup Plugin </a>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Final Thoughts</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is crucial to note that each WordPress plugin has its pros and cons. So take the time to research each one of them carefully to ensure you understand how it works. Also, regardless of the plugin you opt for, make sure to never store your backups on the same server as your website. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>We highly recommend backing up your data on a third-party storage service like Amazon S3, Dropbox, and Google Drive.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-backup-plugins/\">8 Best WordPress Backup Plugins 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/GHBl9yv_XHg\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-backup-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-backup-plugins/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"10 Best Google Serif Fonts Used in 2020\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wplook/~3/o1cbbEEWTLQ/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://wplook.com/serif-fonts/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 31 Mar 2020 22:52:00 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Collections\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Fonts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Google Fonts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Serif fonts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wplook.com/?p=19723\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:542:\"<p>Google Fonts make it easier for everybody to utilize web text fonts, including professional developers and designers.&#160;Typography is a key segment of website design and the decision of which font to use can have a huge impact on how well they’re received. Bellow, you will find a list of the best Google Serif Fonts used [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/serif-fonts/\">10 Best Google Serif Fonts Used in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Diana\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17004:\"\n<p>Google Fonts make it easier for everybody to utilize web text fonts, including professional developers and designers.&nbsp;Typography is a key segment of website design and the decision of which font to use can have a huge impact on how well they’re received. Bellow, you will find a list of the best Google Serif Fonts used in 2018 that you should check out. Also, you can find out which are the top 10 of <a href=\"https://wplook.com/top-sans-serif-fonts/\">Sans-Serif Fonts</a> used by Web Designers in 2018.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Merriweather</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Merriweather-1024x365.png\" alt=\"Merriweather Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19725\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Merriweather-1024x365.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Merriweather-300x107.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Merriweather-768x274.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Merriweather-600x214.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Merriweather Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Merriweather designed by Sorkin Type was created to be a text face that is nice to read on screens. It includes a very large x height, slightly condensed letterforms, a mild diagonal stress, sturdy serifs and open forms. There is also <a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Merriweather+Sans\">Merriweather Sans</a>, a sans-serif version which closely harmonizes with the weights and styles of this serif family.&nbsp;Merriweather Serif Font is featured in more than 2,900,000 websites and Google API displayed the font over 1.54B times in the last week.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular Pairings with Merriweather: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Open Sans</li><li>Oswald</li><li>Montserrat</li><li>Lato</li><li>Roboto</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Merriweather\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:34px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme/?ref=30\" title=\"Studio 8 WordPress Theme\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/studio8-001.jpg\" alt=\"Studio 8 WordPress Theme\"></a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Playfair Display</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Playfair-Display-1024x330.png\" alt=\"Playfair Display Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19726\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Playfair-Display-1024x330.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Playfair-Display-300x97.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Playfair-Display-768x247.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Playfair-Display-600x193.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Playfair Display Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Playfair Display is designed by Claus Eggers&nbsp;Sørensen&nbsp;a type designer based in Amsterdam, Netherland. Playfair is a transitional design and&nbsp;is featured in more than 3,700,000 websites.&nbsp;Being a Display (large size) design in the transitional genre, functionally and stylistically it can accompany Georgia for body text. It was updated&nbsp;in November 2017 with many small improvements and additional language support.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular Pairings with Playfair Display: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Lato</li><li>Roboto</li><li>\n		<g class=\"gr_ gr_7 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"7\" data-gr-id=\"7\">Raleway</g>\n	</li><li>Oswald</li><li>Open Sans Condensed</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Playfair+Display\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Lora</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/lora-1024x346.png\" alt=\"Lora Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19727\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/lora-1024x346.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/lora-300x101.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/lora-768x260.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/lora-600x203.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Lora Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Lora is an adjusted contemporary serif with roots in calligraphy designed by Cyreal. Technically Lora Serif Font is optimized for screen appearance, and works similarly well in print. Lora is a text typeface with moderate contrast appropriate for body text. &nbsp;A paragraph set in Lora will make a great appearance because of its brushed curves in contrast with driving serifs. The general typographic voice of Lora perfectly conveys the mood of a modern-day story, or an art essay. Lora is very popular, being featured in more than 1,500,000 websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular Pairings with Lora: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Open Sans</li><li>Lato</li><li>\n		<g class=\"gr_ gr_7 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"7\" data-gr-id=\"7\">Raleway</g>\n	</li><li>Montserrat</li><li>Roboto</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Lora\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>PT Serif</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/PT-Serif-1024x303.png\" alt=\"PT Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19728\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/PT-Serif-1024x303.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/PT-Serif-300x89.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/PT-Serif-768x227.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/PT-Serif-600x177.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> PT Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The principal designer of PT Serif is ParaType, which was established in 1998 as a successor to the ParaGraph International type department.&nbsp;The fonts include standard Western, Central European and Cyrillic code pages, plus the characters of every title language in the Russian Federation. &nbsp;It is designed for use together with PT Sans, and is harmonized across metrics, proportions, weights, and design. The family consists of six styles: regular and bold weights with corresponding italics form a standard font family for basic text setting; two caption styles in regular and italic are for use in small point sizes.&nbsp;PT Serif is featured in more than 1,000,000 websites and has its well-deserved place in the Best Google Serif Fonts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular Pairings with PT Serif: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Open Sans</li><li>PT Sans</li><li>Roboto</li><li>Source Sans Pro</li><li>Oswald</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/PT+Serif\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Noto Serif</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Noto-Serif-1024x444.png\" alt=\"Noto Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19729\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Noto-Serif-1024x444.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Noto-Serif-300x130.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Noto-Serif-768x333.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Noto-Serif-600x260.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Noto Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Featured in more than 550,000 websites and designed by Google, Noto Serif Noto helps to make the web more beautiful across platforms for all languages.&nbsp;Presently, Noto covers over 30 scripts, and will cover all of Unicode in the future. This is the Serif Latin, Greek and Cyrillic family. It has Regular, Bold, Italic and Bold Italic styles and is hinted. Noto fonts are intended to be visually harmonious across multiple languages, with compatible heights and stroke thicknesses.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular Pairings with Noto Serif: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Noto Sans</li><li>Inconsolata</li><li>Open Sans</li><li>Lato</li><li>Roboto</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Noto+Serif\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Bitter</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Bitter-1024x221.png\" alt=\"Bitter Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19730\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Bitter-1024x221.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Bitter-300x65.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Bitter-768x166.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Bitter-600x130.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Bitter Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Bitter is designed by Sol Matas &nbsp;Huerta for Huerta Tipográfica from Argentina. This font is specially designed to easily and pleasantly read on any computer or device. Bitter has little variation in stroke weight and the Regular is thicker than a normal ‘Regular’ style for print design. This generates an intense color in paragraphs, accentuated by the serifs that are as thick as strokes with square terminals. Each glyph is carefully designed with an excellent curve quality added to the first stage of the design, that was entirely made in a pixel grid. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The typeface is balanced and manually spaced to use very few kerning pairs, especially important for web font use since most browsers do not currently support this feature.&nbsp;Bitter is featured in more than 710,000 websites&nbsp;and&nbsp;Google API displayed the font over 309M times in the last week.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular Pairings with Bitter: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Open Sans</li><li>Source Sans Pro</li><li>Roboto</li><li>Lato</li><li>Oswaldo</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Bitter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Crimson Text</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Crimson--1024x199.png\" alt=\"Crimson Text Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19731\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Crimson--1024x199.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Crimson--300x58.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Crimson--768x149.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Crimson--600x117.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Crimson Text Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Crimson Text is a popular font, designed by Sebastian Kosch.&nbsp;This font family is specially created for book production in the tradition of beautiful old style typefaces. &nbsp;Crimson Text is featured in more than 450,000 websites and is very popular in the USA.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular Pairings with Crimson Text: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Open Sans</li><li>Lato</li><li>\n		<g class=\"gr_ gr_7 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"7\" data-gr-id=\"7\">Raleway</g>\n	</li><li>Roboto</li><li>Lora</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Crimson+Text\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Arvo</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/arvo-1024x214.png\" alt=\"Arvo Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19732\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/arvo-1024x214.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/arvo-300x63.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/arvo-768x160.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/arvo-600x125.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Arvo Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The principal designer of Arvo is Anton Koovit. &nbsp;In the Finnish language, Arvo means &#8220;number, value, worth.&#8221; Considering how much programming was engaged with implying it, that meanings are also significant. Arvo is a geometric slab-serif typeface family suitable for screen and print. This kind of the textual style of the font is rather mixed, being nearly monolinear to expand legibility. &nbsp;Arvo is featured in more than 700,000 websites and this kind of Serif is the most popular in the USA.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular pairings with Arvo</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Open Sans</li><li>Lato</li><li>Roboto</li><li>Oswald</li><li>\n		<g class=\"gr_ gr_7 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"7\" data-gr-id=\"7\">Raleway</g>\n	</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Arvo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Libre Baskerville</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Libre-Baskerville-1024x247.png\" alt=\"Libre Baskerville Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19733\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Libre-Baskerville-1024x247.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Libre-Baskerville-300x72.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Libre-Baskerville-768x185.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Libre-Baskerville-600x145.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Libre Baskerville Serif Font</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Libre Baskerville has been designed by&nbsp;Impallari Type. Libre Baskerville is a web font optimized for body text (typically 16px.) It is based on the American Type Founder&#8217;s Baskerville from 1941, yet it has a taller x-height, wider counters, and somewhat less contrast, that enable it to function great for reading on-screen.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Libre Baskerville is featured in more than 3,000,000 websites and&nbsp;Google API displayed the font over 263M times in the last week&nbsp;and&nbsp;Google API displayed the font over 263M times in the last week.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular pairings with Libre Baskerville</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Poppins</li><li>Lato</li><li>Roboto</li><li>Oswald</li><li>Playfair Display</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Libre+Baskerville?selection.family=Lato|Open+Sans|Poppins\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cormorant Garamond</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Cormorant-Garamond-1024x296.png\" alt=\"Cormorant Garamond Serif Font\" class=\"wp-image-19734\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Cormorant-Garamond-1024x296.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Cormorant-Garamond-300x87.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Cormorant-Garamond-768x222.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Cormorant-Garamond-600x174.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>Cormorant Garamond Serif Font</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Christian Thalmann is the name of the person who developed this free display type family. This kind of Serif is featured in more than 2,000,000 websites and it is the most popular in the USA. &nbsp;The project currently contains a total of 45 font files spanning 9 distinctive visual styles (Roman, Italic, Infant, Infant Italic, Garamond, Garamond Italic, Upright Cursive, Small Caps, and Unicase) and 5 weights (Light, Regular, Medium, SemiBold, and Bold).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Popular pairings with Libre Baskerville</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Lato, Roboto</li><li>Playfair Display</li><li>Oswald</li><li>\n		<g class=\"gr_ gr_6 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"6\" data-gr-id=\"6\">Raleway</g>\n	</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Cormorant+Garamond\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More</a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/serif-fonts/\">10 Best Google Serif Fonts Used in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/o1cbbEEWTLQ\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"https://wplook.com/serif-fonts/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\