(88, 1, '2018-11-03 05:55:13', '2018-11-03 05:55:13', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">OUR MISSION</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thiruvalluvar Nagar Friends Charitable Trust (TNFCT) is a registered, non-profit, independent organization established on 25th September, 2015. The Trust consists of 22 trustees.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The brain behind starting this trust is a group of like-minded friends, who have grown up together in the same neighborhood; presently residing in various locations across and outside the country.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Trust was formed with the moto to \"Empower Underprivileged Children and Elderly\".</p>', 'History & Mission', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'history-mission', '', '', '2019-03-27 01:04:32', '2019-03-27 01:04:32', '', 0, 'http://tnfct.org/?page_id=88', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(89, 1, '2018-11-03 05:55:13', '2018-11-03 05:55:13', '<h4>WHAT WE DO\r\nOn behalf of TNFCT, we are performing various social activities which include:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Plantation on road side with proper local body permission</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide essential supplies to local government schools</li>\r\n 	<li>Distribute meals to kids in local orphanage on festival occasions</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Provide financial aid for financially deprived children--to enable them to resume their education without any hindrance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Besides these, our Trust\'s primary focus is \"Balavica\"--a school for special children</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Serve these \"gifted\" children depending on their needs to enable them to lead a normal life</li>\r\n</ul>', 'What We Do', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-we-do', '', '', '2019-03-27 00:58:36', '2019-03-27 00:58:36', '', 0, 'http://tnfct.org/?page_id=89', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(91, 1, '2018-11-03 05:55:14', '2018-11-03 05:55:14', '<div id=\"pl-91\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-91-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-91-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-91-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">BALAVICA</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">\"<strong>Balavica</strong>\", a school for special children and also a unit of TNFCT, was established as social initiative to serve the children in need with all kinds of developmental disabilities such as ASD (autistic spectrum disorder), CP, MR, Down Syndrome.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n</p></div>\n</div></div><div id=\"panel-91-0-0-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" >[siteorigin_widget class=\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Image_Widget\"]<input type=\"hidden\" value=\"{&quot;instance&quot;:{&quot;image&quot;:255,&quot;image_fallback&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;title_align&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title_position&quot;:&quot;hidden&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bound&quot;:true,&quot;_sow_form_id&quot;:&quot;3388261085bf9d5b0e399a160220923&quot;,&quot;_sow_form_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1543099832385&quot;,&quot;new_window&quot;:false,&quot;full_width&quot;:false,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;sow-image-9110001&quot;,&quot;option_name&quot;:&quot;widget_sow-image&quot;},&quot;args&quot;:{&quot;before_widget&quot;:&quot;&lt;div id=\\&quot;panel-91-0-0-1\\&quot; clas