(144, 1, '2018-11-05 04:55:32', '2018-11-05 04:55:32', '<div id=\"pl-144\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-144-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-144-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.5\" ><div id=\"panel-144-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h1>Our Chennai based Charitable Trust was founded in 2015 by a group of like-minded individuals who have called the area in and around Thirurvalluvar Nagar, Kodungaiyur, Chennai, home for decades.</h1>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-144-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.5\" ><div id=\"panel-144-0-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>WHAT ARE WE DOING?</strong></h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We have come together and formed this trust with the mission of supporting and improving the lives of <em><strong>Children</strong></em> and <em><strong>Elderly</strong></em>, the two most disadvantaged groups in society, in as many ways as we can.</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We also pledge to improve the environment by planting <em><strong>Trees</strong></em> and educating people about the importance of keeping our <em><strong>Surroundings</strong></em> clean.</h3>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-144-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-144-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-144-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h1>We offer more than supplies – we offer <em><strong>HOPE</strong></em>.</h1>\n<h1>We use donor contributions to improve the lives of children today and help establish a promising future for them.</h1>\n<h1><strong><em>We Plant a Better Tomorrow.</em></strong></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h1>Education</h1>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h1>Food</h1>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h1>Clothing</h1>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h1>Planting of trees</h1>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-144-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-144-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-144-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" >[siteorigin_widget class=\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Headline_Widget\"]<input type=\"hidde