 center;\">We also pledge to improve the environment by planting trees and educating people about the importance of keeping our surroundings clean.</h3>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-144-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-144-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-144-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_custom_html panel-first-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" >[siteorigin_widget class=\"WP_Widget_Custom_HTML\"]<input type=\"hidden\" value=\"{&quot;instance&quot;:{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;We offer more than supplies \\u2013 we offer hope.&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;We offer more than supplies \\u2013 we offer hope.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n&lt;p&gt;We use donor contributions to make a difference in the lives of children today, tomorrow, and well into the future. We Plant a Better Tomorrow.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\n&lt;ul&gt;\\n\\t\\t\\t&lt;li&gt;Education&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t\\t\\t&lt;li&gt;Food&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t\\t\\t&lt;li&gt;Clothing&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n\\t\\t\\t&lt;li&gt;Platning of tress&lt;\\/li&gt;\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;custom_html-22910002&quot;,&quot;option_name&quot;:&quot;widget_custom_html&quot;},&quot;args&quot;:{&quot;before_widget&quot;:&quot;&lt;div id=\\&quot;panel-144-1-0-0\\&quot; class=\\&quot;so-panel widget widget_custom_html panel-first-child\\&quot; data-index=\\&quot;2\\&quot; data-style=\\&quot;{&amp;quot;background_image_attachment&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;background_display&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;tile&amp;quot;}\\&quot; &gt;&quot;,&quot;after_widget&quot;:&quot;&lt;\\/div&gt;&quot;,&quot;before_title&quot;:&quot;&lt;h3 class=\\&quot;widget-title\\&quot;&gt;&