(263, 2, '2019-03-27 00:58:07', '2019-03-27 00:58:07', '<h4>WHAT WE DO\nOn behalf of TNFCT, we are performing various social activities which include:</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Plantation on road side with proper local body permission</li>\n 	<li>Provide essential supplies to local government schools</li>\n 	<li>Distribute meals to kids in local orphanage on festival occasions</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Provide financial aid for financially deprived children--to enable them to resume their education without any hindrance.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Besides these, our Trust\'s primary focus is \"Balavica\"--a school for special children</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Serve these \"gifted\" children depending on their needs to enable them to lead a normal life</li>\n</ul>', 'What We Do', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '89-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-03-27 00:58:07', '2019-03-27 00:58:07', '', 89, 'http://tnfct.org/2019/03/27/89-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(264, 2, '2019-03-27 00:58:36', '2019-03-27 00:58:36', '<h4>WHAT WE DO\r\nOn behalf of TNFCT, we are performing various social activities which include:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Plantation on road side with proper local body permission</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide essential supplies to local government schools</li>\r\n 	<li>Distribute meals to kids in local orphanage on festival occasions</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Provide financial aid for financially deprived children--to enable them to resume their education without any hindrance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Besides these, our Trust\'s primary focus is \"Balavica\"--a school for special children</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Serve these \"gifted\" children depending on their needs to enable them to lead a normal life</li>\r\n</ul>', 'What We Do', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '89-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-27 00:58:36', '2019-03-27 00:58:36', '', 89, 'http://tnfct.org/2019/03/27/89-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(265, 2, '2019-03-27 01:04:16', '2019-03-27 01:04:16', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">OUR MISSION</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thiruvalluvar Nagar Friends Charitable Trust (TNFCT) is a registered, non-profit, independent organization established on 25th September, 2015. The Trust consists of 22 trustees.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The brain behind starting this trust is a group of like-minded friends, who have grown up together in the same neighborhood; presently residing in various locations across and outside the country.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Trust was formed with the moto to \"Empower Underprivileged Children and Elderly\".</p>', 'History & Mission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '88-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-03-27 01:04:16', '2019-03-27 01:04:16', '', 88, 'http://tnfct.org/2019/03/27/88-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(266, 2, '2019-03-27 01:04:32', '2019-03-27 01:04:32', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">OUR MISSION</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thiruvalluvar Nagar Friends Charitable Trust (TNFCT) is a registered, non-profit, independent organization established on 25th September, 2015. The Trust consists of 22 trustees.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The brain behind starting this trust is a group of like-minded friends, who have grown up together in the same neighborhood; presently residing in various locations across and outside the country.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Trust was formed with the moto to \"Empower Underprivileged Children and Elderly\".</p>', 'History & Mission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '88-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-03-27 01:04:32', '2019-03-27 01:04:32', '', 88, 'http://tnfct.org/2019/03/27/88-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(267, 2, '2019-03-27 01:06:14', '2019-03-27 01:06:14', '<div id=\"pl-144\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-144-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-144-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.5\" ><div id=\"panel-144-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h1>Our Chennai based Charitable Trust was founded in 2015 by a group of like-minded individuals who have called the area in and around Thirurvalluvar Nagar, Kodungaiyur, Chennai, home for decades.</h1>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-144-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.5\" ><div id=\"panel-144-0-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>WHAT ARE WE DOING?</strong></h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We have come together and formed this trust with the mission of supporting and improving the lives of Children and Elderly, the two most disadvantaged groups in society, in as many ways as we can.</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We also pledge to improve the enviro